  "pageTitle": "大件废弃物预处理参考案例",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-industrial\"> <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">大件废弃物案例</p> <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">大件废弃物预处理参考案例</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">参考适用于采购方需要在一个工作流程中完成接收、体积缩小、分离和打包废料的紧凑型废弃物预处理。</p></section> <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout\" aria-labelledby=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout-timeline-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">系统流程</p> <h2 id=\"bulky-waste-processing-layout-timeline-title\">案例范围展示大件废弃物处理的紧凑预处理布局</h2> <p>案例按项目评估流程排序：背景、合作单位、限制、解决方案以及前后对比。</p></div> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例流程时间线\"> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">项目背景</p> <h3>超大件物料处理压力</h3> <p>该布局通过缩小进料尺寸、分离可回收组分以及准备残渣以便下游处理，处理大件废弃物和轻质混合废弃物。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>物料类别</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 类物料流</strong><span>体积大且轻的混合废弃物</span></dd></div> <div><dt>目标路线</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 套流程</strong><span>接收到打包输出</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作单位</p> <h3>转运站运营场景</h3> <p>合作单位计划减少大件废弃物运输量，并在最终处置或下游转移前回收可回收组分。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>操作人员类型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 环卫团队</strong><span>转运站运营</span></dd></div> <div><dt>项目关注点</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 目标</strong><span>减容与回收</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">实际限制</p> <h3>转运站占地限制</h3> <p>该场地需要接收区、大型物料分拣区、设备通道、回收组分储存区和卡车装载区，且操作空间紧凑。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>场地分区</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 个区域</strong><span>从接收区到装载区</span></dd></div> <div><dt>布局类型</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">紧凑型</strong><span>单一工作流程路径</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解决方案</p> <h3>分离与打包接口</h3> <p>工艺范围结合了破碎、筛分、气流分离、输送、选配磁选、打包接口以及远程控制支持。</p> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>流程模块</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 个模块</strong><span>破碎 / 筛分 / 气流 / 输送</span></dd></div> <div><dt>接口</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 个接口</strong><span>打包与遥控</span></dd></div></dl></div></article> <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\"> <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div> <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\"> <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前后对比</p> <h3>可控预处理路径</h3> <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\"> <div><span>之前</span><strong>超大废料以松散混合物质的形式流动</strong><p>在减小尺寸和回收检查前，运输和暂存压力一直很高。</p></div> <div><span>之后</span><strong>减容、分离，准备下游处理</strong><p>参考视频展示了送料、破碎、气流分离、排放和打包界面的流程。</p></div></div> <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\"> <div><dt>视频范围</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">5 个步骤</strong><span>进料到打包接口</span></dd></div></dl></div></article></div></section> <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section industrial-rfq-section ai-layout-reference\" aria-label=\"案例操作\"> <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求参考包</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回参考案例</a></div></section></main>"
}
